Package: RcppRNGParallel
Title: Independent Parallel Random Number Streams with dqrng
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "James",
           family = "Balamuta",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "balamut2@illinois.edu")
Description: Shows how to draw random numbers in parallel with independent,
    reproducible streams by giving each thread its own substream of a single
    seeded 'dqrng' generator.
